{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_011GeEi1Mb7LBedhxhBFGXGB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01NpR7y8VRjqNa6EyTXMWpNx","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Read and validate vendor workbook","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. Read the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - get ALL rows including headers\n2. Read the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - get all content\n3. Read the \"Methodology\" sheet - get all content  \n4. Read the \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - get all content\n\nUse the following Node.js script to extract data. Run it via Bash:\n\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path, {cellStyles: true, cellFormula: true, sheetStubs: true});\n\nconsole.log('Sheet names:', wb.SheetNames);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconst ws = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (ws) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ws, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  console.log('\\n=== Vendor Analysis Assessment ===');\n  console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n  // Print first 5 rows to see structure\n  console.log('First 5 rows:');\n  for (let i = 0; i < Math.min(5, data.length); i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n  // Print all rows from row 2 onwards (vendor data)\n  console.log('\\nAll vendor rows (row index 2+):');\n  for (let i = 2; i < data.length; i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n}\n\n// Read other sheets\n['Top 3 Opportunities', 'Methodology', 'CEOCFO Recommendations'].forEach(sheetName => {\n  const s = wb.Sheets[sheetName];\n  if (s) {\n    const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(s, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n    console.log('\\n=== ' + sheetName + ' ===');\n    console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n    data.forEach((row, i) => {\n      console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(row));\n    });\n  }\n});\n```\n\nSave the script to C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/read_workbook.js and run it with node.\n\nReturn ALL the output - every single row. Do not truncate."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1974,"cache_read_input_tokens":14418,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1974,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"58a9a62f-a2c0-4284-b72f-83f7f441309c","uuid":"09fbd5f8-61d3-4015-8b04-26130b38daa1"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"a9c198a4fc667302c","tool_use_id":"toolu_01NpR7y8VRjqNa6EyTXMWpNx","description":"Read and validate vendor workbook","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. Read the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - get ALL rows including headers\n2. Read the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - get all content\n3. Read the \"Methodology\" sheet - get all content  \n4. Read the \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - get all content\n\nUse the following Node.js script to extract data. Run it via Bash:\n\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path, {cellStyles: true, cellFormula: true, sheetStubs: true});\n\nconsole.log('Sheet names:', wb.SheetNames);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconst ws = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (ws) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ws, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  console.log('\\n=== Vendor Analysis Assessment ===');\n  console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n  // Print first 5 rows to see structure\n  console.log('First 5 rows:');\n  for (let i = 0; i < Math.min(5, data.length); i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n  // Print all rows from row 2 onwards (vendor data)\n  console.log('\\nAll vendor rows (row index 2+):');\n  for (let i = 2; i < data.length; i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n}\n\n// Read other sheets\n['Top 3 Opportunities', 'Methodology', 'CEOCFO Recommendations'].forEach(sheetName => {\n  const s = wb.Sheets[sheetName];\n  if (s) {\n    const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(s, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n    console.log('\\n=== ' + sheetName + ' ===');\n    console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n    data.forEach((row, i) => {\n      console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(row));\n    });\n  }\n});\n```\n\nSave the script to C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/read_workbook.js and run it with node.\n\nReturn ALL the output - every single row. Do not truncate.","uuid":"6d843811-2e75-4d58-8f2f-b2183f09bb47","session_id":"58a9a62f-a2c0-4284-b72f-83f7f441309c"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. Read the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - get ALL rows including headers\n2. Read the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - get all content\n3. Read the \"Methodology\" sheet - get all content  \n4. Read the \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - get all content\n\nUse the following Node.js script to extract data. Run it via Bash:\n\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path, {cellStyles: true, cellFormula: true, sheetStubs: true});\n\nconsole.log('Sheet names:', wb.SheetNames);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconst ws = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (ws) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ws, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  console.log('\\n=== Vendor Analysis Assessment ===');\n  console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n  // Print first 5 rows to see structure\n  console.log('First 5 rows:');\n  for (let i = 0; i < Math.min(5, data.length); i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n  // Print all rows from row 2 onwards (vendor data)\n  console.log('\\nAll vendor rows (row index 2+):');\n  for (let i = 2; i < data.length; i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n}\n\n// Read other sheets\n['Top 3 Opportunities', 'Methodology', 'CEOCFO Recommendations'].forEach(sheetName => {\n  const s = wb.Sheets[sheetName];\n  if (s) {\n    const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(s, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n    console.log('\\n=== ' + sheetName + ' ===');\n    console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n    data.forEach((row, i) => {\n      console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(row));\n    });\n  }\n});\n```\n\nSave the script to C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/read_workbook.js and run it with node.\n\nReturn ALL the output - every single row. Do not truncate."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01NpR7y8VRjqNa6EyTXMWpNx","session_id":"58a9a62f-a2c0-4284-b72f-83f7f441309c","uuid":"6cd222f4-f436-4375-b7f6-1be368246c0e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:42:14.912Z"}
