{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NpR7y8VRjqNa6EyTXMWpNx","type":"tool_result","content":"<persisted-output>\nOutput too large (53.3KB). Full output saved to: C:\\Users\\rjega\\.claude\\projects\\C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis\\58a9a62f-a2c0-4284-b72f-83f7f441309c\\tool-results\\toolu_01NpR7y8VRjqNa6EyTXMWpNx.json\n\nPreview (first 2KB):\n[\n  {\n    \"type\": \"text\",\n    \"text\": \"Here is the complete output from all four sheets:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Sheet Names\\n1. Vendor Analysis Assessment\\n2. Top 3 Opportunities\\n3. Methodology\\n4. CEOCFO Recommendations\\n5. Config\\n6. First Quick Analysis\\n7. STEP08 Strategic Scores\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Vendor Analysis Assessment\\n**Total rows: 387** (1 header row + 386 vendor rows)\\n\\n**Header (Row 0):**\\n`Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\\n\\n**All vendor rows (Row 1 = first data row, which is \\\"(Blank)\\\"):**\\n\\n| Row | Vendor Name | Department | Cost (USD) | Description | Suggestion |\\n|-----|------------|-----------|-----------|-------------|-----------|\\n| 1 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Unidentified vendor with no name or clear purpose | Terminate |\\n| 2 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Management advisory firm providing strategic consulting services | Consolidate |\\n| 3 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Management consulting firm overlapping with 4I Advisory Services | Consolidate |\\n| 4 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Promotional merchandise supplier for branded marketing materials | Terminate |\\n| 5 | 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | AI-powered revenue intelligence platform for B2B marketing | Terminate |\\n| 6 | Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Corporate services provider for entity management and compliance | Consolidate |\\n| 7 | Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | US entity of Acclime providing corporate administration services | Consolidate |\\n| 8 | Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Graduate trainee recruitment and placement services | Terminate |\\n| 9 | Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Back-office information services provider | Terminate |\\n| 10 | Adobe Systems Software | S\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"58a9a62f-a2c0-4284-b72f-83f7f441309c","uuid":"ef591c2c-4e7f-4a4d-ab71-8abd8fdc9f72","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:48:06.180Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Excel workbook at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\n\nI need you to:\n1. Read the \"Vendor Analysis Assessment\" sheet - get ALL rows including headers\n2. Read the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet - get all content\n3. Read the \"Methodology\" sheet - get all content  \n4. Read the \"CEOCFO Recommendations\" sheet - get all content\n\nUse the following Node.js script to extract data. Run it via Bash:\n\n```javascript\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\nconst path = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(path, {cellStyles: true, cellFormula: true, sheetStubs: true});\n\nconsole.log('Sheet names:', wb.SheetNames);\n\n// Read Vendor Analysis Assessment\nconst ws = wb.Sheets['Vendor Analysis Assessment'];\nif (ws) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(ws, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n  console.log('\\n=== Vendor Analysis Assessment ===');\n  console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n  // Print first 5 rows to see structure\n  console.log('First 5 rows:');\n  for (let i = 0; i < Math.min(5, data.length); i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n  // Print all rows from row 2 onwards (vendor data)\n  console.log('\\nAll vendor rows (row index 2+):');\n  for (let i = 2; i < data.length; i++) {\n    console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(data[i]));\n  }\n}\n\n// Read other sheets\n['Top 3 Opportunities', 'Methodology', 'CEOCFO Recommendations'].forEach(sheetName => {\n  const s = wb.Sheets[sheetName];\n  if (s) {\n    const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(s, {header: 1, defval: ''});\n    console.log('\\n=== ' + sheetName + ' ===');\n    console.log('Total rows:', data.length);\n    data.forEach((row, i) => {\n      console.log('Row ' + i + ':', JSON.stringify(row));\n    });\n  }\n});\n```\n\nSave the script to C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/read_workbook.js and run it with node.\n\nReturn ALL the output - every single row. Do not truncate.","agentId":"a9c198a4fc667302c","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is the complete output from all four sheets:\n\n---\n\n## Sheet Names\n1. Vendor Analysis Assessment\n2. Top 3 Opportunities\n3. Methodology\n4. CEOCFO Recommendations\n5. Config\n6. First Quick Analysis\n7. STEP08 Strategic Scores\n\n---\n\n## Vendor Analysis Assessment\n**Total rows: 387** (1 header row + 386 vendor rows)\n\n**Header (Row 0):**\n`Vendor Name | Department | Last 12 months Cost (USD) | 1-line Description on what the Vendor does | Suggestions (Consolidate / Terminate / Optimize costs) | DERIVED-Spend Category`\n\n**All vendor rows (Row 1 = first data row, which is \"(Blank)\"):**\n\n| Row | Vendor Name | Department | Cost (USD) | Description | Suggestion |\n|-----|------------|-----------|-----------|-------------|-----------|\n| 1 | (Blank) | G&A | 137.30 | Unidentified vendor with no name or clear purpose | Terminate |\n| 2 | 4I Advisory Services | Professional Services | 71,860.34 | Management advisory firm providing strategic consulting services | Consolidate |\n| 3 | 4I Management Consulting Private Limited | Professional Services | 12,117.49 | Management consulting firm overlapping with 4I Advisory Services | Consolidate |\n| 4 | 4Imprint Direct Ltd | Marketing | 2,436.14 | Promotional merchandise supplier for branded marketing materials | Terminate |\n| 5 | 6Sense Insights Inc | Marketing | 75.56 | AI-powered revenue intelligence platform for B2B marketing | Terminate |\n| 6 | Acclime Corporate Services | G&A | 5,412.87 | Corporate services provider for entity management and compliance | Consolidate |\n| 7 | Acclime Usa, Inc | G&A | 4,994.98 | US entity of Acclime providing corporate administration services | Consolidate |\n| 8 | Accutrainee Limited | Professional Services | 38,840.80 | Graduate trainee recruitment and placement services | Terminate |\n| 9 | Adamma Info Services Private Limited | G&A | 273.33 | Back-office information services provider | Terminate |\n| 10 | Adobe Systems Software | SaaS | 3,928.65 | Creative software suite for design and document management | Terminate |\n| 11 | Advena | G&A | 153.89 | Unknown vendor with negligible spend and unclear purpose | Terminate |\n| 12 | Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | G&A | 124,661.46 | Group health and life insurance provider for employee benefits | Optimize |\n| 13 | Ag Grid Ltd | Engineering | 2,653.27 | High-performance data grid library for web application development | Terminate |\n| 14 | Agram Life Osiguranje D.O.O. | G&A | 24,952.20 | Croatian life insurance provider for employee group policies | Terminate |\n| 15 | Aha! Labs Inc | Product | 3,689.33 | Product roadmap and strategy management platform | Consolidate |\n| 16 | Akton D.O.O. | Facilities | 3,253.58 | Croatian facilities services vendor | Terminate |\n| 17 | Allianz Australia Workers' Compensation (Victoria) Limited | HR | 6,098.63 | Workers compensation insurance for Australian employees | Optimize |\n| 18 | Allianz Wa | G&A | 970.71 | Allianz Western Australia workers compensation insurance entity | Consolidate |\n| 19 | Amazon (Aus) | G&A | 233.31 | General procurement from Amazon Australia for office supplies | Terminate |\n| 20 | Amazon Web Servic